reload, and then you have

00:09:30.750 --> 00:09:35.300
these nice splash effects that
happen on the screen.

00:09:35.300 --> 00:09:39.080
It sort of makes me feel like
they used the engine from the

00:09:39.080 --> 00:09:44.300
original "Wolfenstein 3D" here
in terms of complexity.

00:09:44.300 --> 00:09:46.170
But hey, it works.

