actually having to move my gun

00:10:12.600 --> 00:10:13.920
with a virtual joystick.

00:10:13.920 --> 00:10:16.480
At this point, I just want to
go tap, tap, tap, tap, tap.

00:10:16.480 --> 00:10:17.720
IAN NI-LEWIS: Yeah, what's
up with that?

00:10:17.720 --> 00:10:18.910
What is up with that,
seriously?

00:10:18.910 --> 00:10:19.850
DAN GALPIN: I know, I now.

00:10:19.850 --> 00:10:21.610
IAN NI-LEWIS: Right?

00:10:21.610 --> 00:10:22.810
DAN GALPIN: But I wanted to
mention it because it was

00:10:22.810 --> 00:10:25.210
actually a nicely themed
Halloween game.

